<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on&nbsp;</b><span style="line-height: 18px;"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</b></span></font></div><div><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></span></b></div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c},</span><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">It is possible that you will incur expenses during your assignment with The Challenge. Please use this form to submit all expenses.&nbsp;</span></font><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Ensure you keep all receipts for any expense you incur as we will be unable to repay any expenses without receipts.&nbsp;</span><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><a href="http://www.clicktools.com/survey?iv=1ynqaok0qujan&amp;q1={!Job_Application__c.Id}&amp;q2={!Job_placement__c.Id}">Expenses form</a></span></font><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b style="line-height: 18px;">Please read the instructions carefully:</b><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Expenses will be paid to you on a monthly basis and need to be submitted before the third Sunday of the month to avoid delays to repayment.</span><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"><br clear="none" style="line-height: 18px;"></font><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><strong><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">How do I claim expenses?</font></strong></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Claiming expenses is very easy. Just follow these steps:</font></div><ol style="padding: 0px 40px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Scan or photograph your receipts from the summer.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Number the scans/photographs to correspond to the items on the form.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Itemise your expenses and upload scans or photographs of your receipts on the online form.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Submit the form</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Send your receipts to&nbsp;<a data-cke-saved-href="mailto:programme.expenses@the-challenge.org" href="mailto:programme.expenses@the-challenge.org"><span style="color: rgb(165, 42, 42);"><strong>programme.expenses@the-challenge.org</strong></span></a></font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The form can be re-used for further claims</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please ensure you retain all receipts until you have been paid your expenses.&nbsp;</font></li></ol><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">If you are submitting expenses for more than one part of The Challenge, please do so on separate forms.&nbsp;</span><br type="_moz" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></font><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We will only authorise expenses for essential travel during the programme.&nbsp;This&nbsp;<strong>does not</strong>&nbsp;cover your travel to or from your place of residence and The Challenge venues.<br><font>Our Expenses Policy only covers 'other' expenses in exceptional circumstances.&nbsp;</font>Please note that we will be unable to repay any expenses without receipts.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br><font style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">We can only accept scanned or clearly photographed receipts. Paper receipts handed in or posted will not be processed.</span></font></font><div style="text-align: -webkit-auto;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br>We encourage you to submit your expenses regularly - on a weekly basis where possible. This will help to ensure you are reimbursed as quickly as possible.</font></div><div style="text-align: -webkit-auto;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Your claim will be authorised if everything is completed correctly. We will aim to pay all expenses directly into your bank account within two weeks of receiving your claim.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The deadline for the submission of expenses is 31 October 2013. Any expenses submitted after this date will not be paid.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">If you have any questions please contact your local staffing representative.</span></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Best wishes,&nbsp;</span></font><div><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate__c}</font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">The Challenge&nbsp;</font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></div><div><span style="line-height: 18px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">CR 2.2.2</font></span></div></div></div>]]></td>
